<article id="post-766" class="post-766 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-travel tag-air-canada tag-huntsville tag-ontario tag-weddings">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/07/a-middle-ontario-wedding/" rel="bookmark">A Middle Ontario wedding</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><a href="http://www.sowrey.org/photos/wedding/kathryn-and-andreas-wedding/">My friend Kathryn got married this weekend.</a> A truly wonderful event that forced my hand to leave the comfort of my familiar Cowtown (and miss the opening of the Calgary Stampede) to visit rural Ontario and experience the joyous event.<br />
I gotta say, probably the most relaxful weekend I&#8217;ve had in &#8230; well, a really long time.<br />
