	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/07/up-at-the-cottage/" rel="bookmark">Up at the cottage</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Over the weekend, I had the chance to go stay with my sister and brother-in-law&#8217;s cottage near Huntsville, ON. It&#8217;s been a long time since I was last there, and it was good to see my family one last time before it expands again by one.<br />
I really need to get out there more often.<br />
